      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, always kept it in the garage and pampered it. It drives like a dream and still has that new car smell! If you're looking for perfection, this is the one. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to love it as much as I do. Shoot me a message if you want to take a look!",
