      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a pristine example of naturally aspirated precision. It features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and an optimized double-VANOS system for razor-sharp throttle response. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides short, mechanical throws, sending power to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is absolute, with a reinforced rear subframe and original bushings maintaining factory-spec lateral stiffness. Rod bearings and the high-pressure VANOS system have been meticulously maintained within strict tolerances, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline remains as potent as the day it left Regensburg. This is a collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance.",
